      "content": "it just seems so extreme to say a single glass can be dangerous. i've had it before and felt fine. are you sure it's that serious? like, i'm not worried about it being 'toxic', i just want to know if it actually interferes with the medicine working. if it's just a tiny bit, can i just take the pill a few hours after the juice so there's no direct contact?",
